OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud and rain easing to
OL,6,Fleave sunny spells. Some showers
OL,7,Fremain, mostly in the north and west.
OL,8,FA little cooler than Friday but
OL,9,Ftemperatures still above average in
OL,10,Fsouth and southeast England. Turning
OL,11,Fbreezy in the far north.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers fading leaving a dry
OL,14,Fnight though thunderstorms may clip
OL,15,Fthe southeast. Feeling fresher for
OL,16,Fsome, but a warm and humid night to
OL,17,Fcome in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
